OL,4,CAccountants: Government to break up
OL,5,Cdominance of Big Four firms
OL,6, Proposals to reduce the dominance of
OL,7, the "Big Four" accountancy firms and
OL,8, scrap the industry regulator have been
OL,9, unveiled by the government.
OL,11,FThe aim is to improve regulatory
OL,12,Fstandards after high profile corporate
OL,13,Ffailures such as Carillion and BHS.
OL,15,FAlso, company directors will face more
OL,16,Fresponsibility to ensure accounts are
OL,17,Faccurate, or face tougher penalties.
OL,19,FBusiness Secretary Kwasi Kwarteng said
OL,20,Fthe changes would help restore
OL,21,Fconfidence in business.
